[{"Name":"Kiariladyboss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCEIQq7u4XLgEzL_AKtN5X92ml-ugV3sa6GTf414nIAAMrrAQF3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a blast and the food was DELICIOUS. Me and my friend visited Shaffa Bar on a Monday night, they had live music from 9pm and they also have live music every Friday from 7pm.

Everything we ordered was so so good from the veggie with focaccia to the tahini , schnitzel was incredible!

Will definitely go back once i’ll visit Tel Aviv again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgdUxUVN9HzJzDPj9S-RrkcdEKmYLKeYmxfwJR&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2023-8-24"},{"Name":"Roman Zelvenschi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBTBXofX0oLr267bOO_jukQNUpUeeiXzD6GnCFeXWMGJXfMD91Cg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Authentic Tel-Aviv atmosphere, friendly service even though our table was a bit complicated with 12 people. Very nice cocktails and actually reasonable prices by Israeli standards. Live DJ and fun crowd.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyxDhysce6b0tkyZEgrSqA-rcWGN_JPu5DwOrd&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Claudia Pridor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaGQrxtwFIuzGDD1u0pxtEAgIsoLfgA8Ya0FTNBB9aWQjhHr9H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience ! Music , people… fun place to chill on a Friday noon. Great food! Will definitely adopt this place ! The whole area is wonderful!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEiBY6eFEjTNeqlmPwbQA4p-zu1ZiK7iaTYvE&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2023-6-24"},{"Name":"Lihi Bavli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDrsJ54hPaascFr9Yiu7t0PP56Szf5z_v0BUYErt3agnvaX5DeMA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I sat there for brunch with my friend on a Friday. As expected it was busy, and a little hot sitting outside, but it was shady. The food is very special and yummy and we really enjoyed it. The yugurthini especially is super special and good. We also had the pink sangria which was really good! I do believe will come back 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQfD-11qv8u7INwZ0KWK0X6uGsMs9YYWiqmtyO&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2021-8-17"},{"Name":"Niro Bitko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMvX0rDx6ztV8IGRIz_mlgFn5T2mE5YG271691rd_9tVPPJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We arrived at the flea market area in Jaffa on a rainy day!  We took shelter in a restaurant, and apparently fate invited us to an experiential morning 😄 The hostess seated us at a table for two located under the shed, so we enjoyed sitting inside the restaurant with the feeling of sitting on the edge of the street.  We ordered shakshuka and salads, we got the food very quickly, even though the restaurant was full.  The food was very tasty and rich.  We asked for more tahini and bread and we got it right away!  The appropriate music blended well with the rain in the background and the voices of the diners.  It was a fun experience, we will come back again!  Not only to take shelter from the rain, but for the food, the service and the atmosphere","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwP5vB3DcQuYrX3xFfp1xrzAD7HaEslz26wUmO&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2022-12-24"},{"Name":"Eric Berberich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWF8hKJUr7Xjti44PYZFQgNqCiE1gn-eMoN2WO5C7a-Y50OuEgnxA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Honestly a bit disappointed. Food was mediocre. Service very slow. Water and drinks came after food. Misunderstood our order... Cocktails ok.. Pity as it's a nice atmosphere in the flea market.. Could be much better","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOCTu7hVtPKZGeC-e6U6dGeJSe-3DNLll4VTnf&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2023-10-2"},{"Name":"Dain Boelter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjjXJt-MNo0LpZBgxJJN9lqhXF0z05mGqgVbj3oIMQHeo7LiHjzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I read some reviews that talked about the Siniya so I decided to get it and I'm glad I did. It was delicious and very flavourful. I would highly recommend it. The chopped liver as a starter was delicious as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOrV0V1T54oGFBT1W5F_jEiK8ms__YfFLSFXDSW&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2020-2-16"},{"Name":"Olivier S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvTbAgO5F1sv8yBBqQXj2__liLfadjlSTwHAMrTFQUmEP8xfM_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stylish bar in Jaffa with an eclectic menu. Laidback staff and a mellow playlist made it a good place to watch the crowds go by.  The pide was delicious and a really generous size.  Liked all this a lot; four stars because it felt a bit expensive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_U32zX9HsCGvfCaC9XIp85KwWZw-1AjJfC5gr&fid=0x0:0x2a4954ab3fef006"],"When":"2022-6-4"}]

[{"Name":"Alex Drukpa.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcjAz32jebBVis0wva7BdfszADkJsUePTz3QCGq89HzR3AgTd_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Like that pub. Been there a few times and everytime we had a great evening. Lots of drinking and eating options. Has a small non smoking area, the larger area is full of smokers. Reasonable prices, not to expensive, that's nice.
Typical kind of crowd, in the evenings, some people will blend in fine.. Some less.. Earlier more tourists. Love the lighting and atmosphere. Have a private viewing room for games and bigger groups.Highly recommended to visit night is better than day time must visit","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJMqSOXr09tvZnY8mh0AdG8I-6GJWuBAIsMG1B&fid=0x0:0x511268eed7324177"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"C A Moss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICvgEk0FeIml_YyUaiRS3p3FzXE1lVKG679Rh0MVm6_kzsCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"On a tour of Israel and was a night on our own. Most places were closed for shabbott. Dublin pub opened at 5p so we had a short walk to the pub. Greeted by a friendly lady who waited on us. Fish and chips were delicious and the Guinness was too. Ordered Israeli IPA and my hubby loved it. The lovely lady served chocolate lava cake and ice cream to share....on her, to welcome to Israel. (We tipped generously) soccer on the telly. Pub atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPy1rIbkQBrrlp_NxZMxn0UjlMbyYxmgaJMkkeD&fid=0x0:0x511268eed7324177"],"When":"2023-1-30"},{"Name":"Gershon Marais","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwg8jBIQbrmAv-rF1h3xAp_LjEIKaX5CyGgwL2Mgzr88QcKA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went there on Sunday evening to watch Football ⚽️. The food and beverages served was good. However, there was a waitress who clearly did not want to be at work or who just doesn't fancy serving tourists as she was rather bubbly with the locals in the pub. She spoilt what should've been a nice night out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4qlzBY7hIDWOsjDCjYu5_ewruoEKHHyXme14U&fid=0x0:0x511268eed7324177"],"When":"2023-8-16"},{"Name":"Robert Amery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXedqaZD1FZmIQjejnSRrvOLmgGuR_n0LL9KzrPXx4YcYTDZ57t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went to watch a football game, great atmosphere,  good music and good choices of beers. The food was ok+, and the service was good in proportion to how full the place was.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM04oNdUcRxvkzFwyMUQmjTgZmH3DxHiY-76mk2&fid=0x0:0x511268eed7324177"],"When":"2022-5-14"},{"Name":"Brian Lowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkMLcRedQtwTHznYhpilCVcShiFIIWwvUSl6URYeTRJ99t3JpI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Always friendly.  A great place for a meal and a few Guinness","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"tova g","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKufzJUlMBlus4D2dhENQB88HENyKdypw3gJOycq5SpRcuPSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the most fun places they got a huge menu full of great options and a really nice vibe the only problem is that everyone one is smoking there and they got this little place for the non-smokers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOu4AT6VnCc1zpPazJ-2FHSIQpTZXx3gtmLbc0Z&fid=0x0:0x511268eed7324177"],"When":"2020-1-15"},{"Name":"Aaro Slutsky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3MHWCzTNE14FGbdWWABtPHnNajL8rcxfwW5Ov5QRurdPj-3rC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very cozy Irish pub. Gentle music playing all around you, a wide variety of beers and a nice food to butter it all up. The interior is gorgeous and really takes you on a spiritual trip to the distant pubs of Dublin.
I took the burger. The chips were really basic, nice and salty, whereas the burger itself was juicy and fresh.
The prices are reasonable.
I really recommend this place if you wanna grab a quiet drinkin a stylish place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMREfHyc_zIcLD3z8HtUZCSmoqxGLs3comIgOYF&fid=0x0:0x511268eed7324177"],"When":"2021-7-28"},{"Name":"Jose Guevarez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJf3mmDUVeb1w_rqbsoZHIWcPfxumpTSqgEPM1pBtRnw3XsaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was very pleasantly surprised to find this bar near my hotel in Jerusalem. The staff is wonderful, the food and drinks were terrific. The service superb and with a great vibe. The owner Shay is a very nice gentlemen who went out of his way to make sure we were having a good time and feeling at home. This is a great hidden gem in Jerusalem.

Jose G","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Oded Kassirer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBVFWcOaiMdQjfS3MGw6Uu6B6JnkcUxFKUJt_-LJhMZl_V51QJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We started with the Artichoke and Labane appetizer and it was absolutely amazing! Great service, beautiful place inside and out. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIj6Dsjm7CO_bHsRdKuoeGNi2XbYuOkI17pwbH&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2022-12-14"},{"Name":"Brandon Jackiewicz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVf7zPhSKW4mU1iMsYzR_h-tg8BzvPJJTkUR8FzgDLNq-SlzxX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just like my stars suggest, this place has amazing food, service and atmosphere. If you're in Jaffa, and you're local or new, morning or all nighter, you will find good times, good food, and good company here. Give it a shot, eat something you haven't before, and trust me... you won't regret it. :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMX1hzWiHKUXc_AuKHewGcX9FaXuWC_j7SCfcU9&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-7-4"},{"Name":"Michael Salaverry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWboG-cAjDxAgnIMS-BkPV34_otrll_mM2Hw_qZOZWcLlumj6kTwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Jaffa party on a Saturday restaurant. They even had a live DJ playing 80s hits. The food was wonderful. We did send the kebab back to get cooked thoroughly, but they were very understanding and professional. Excellent host as well. Highly recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjUYCPYKWYG5pVlm2yuv16cZqNQ5Hl54YUYDow&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"Jane Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURUWPRLP6iBmcwarcBdm2jOIHG1EqApmaiikQEL8Z9ueEMNFKYOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The herb salad and ceviche were fantastic! Exactly what we were looking for our brunch. We also love the eggplant dish with the creamy garlicky sauce. The restaurant was kind enough and get us a chocolate mousse on the house. Very nice ambiance and lively atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMorLVYWY5igYJqjgk7B7tdNSHduza_kbUvQuJh&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2022-5-22"},{"Name":"Cedric Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW--ZYvS6afHrouMBeMebdJQ22d56_9qN7aYKmC-Wf0gfNaGk5y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Located in the Jaffa flea market, this charming restaurant is the perfect spot for a nice dinner with a whole lot of Middle Eastern specialities. The food is really good and the atmosphere around Raisa is great. Strongly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjje1L0LLoRb7WeXDSg6EPp9A4B_X2QSFu6_L-&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-9-8"},{"Name":"Arie Rozichner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsiV5wYoIh-42Le67--Zpaqp7bWXRkKeSkFJxTrObEVQh12ujArQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place with good atmosphere and typical Jaffa ambience. The food is OK. The service is nice, but sometimes slow.
Had Israeli breakfast - good, and Artichoke and Labneh salad - didn't really connected to it - almost no rocket leaves, too much onions and labneh and chips.
Good value for your money.
Recommended mainly for simple food lovers and getting Jaffa atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDswi1bq9vpdiliO1ce0liZMwaIoIkKGin12ub&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-3-24"},{"Name":"Sean Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxhpNxaW7QK7DA2RIwkmtUc3AK45tVorFuYznWmwjUbco6Q8_i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really tasty bread, dips and lamb pitas and cigars. For the price - amazing quality food. Really friendly and funny front of house staff. Great vibes sitting outside watching the world go by. Good music and not too loud so you can still speak comfortably.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPy6uOQDgCU_3ZOkiXffD04LVeXwWYV4r-7L5zT&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Vincent Vasina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbMV4fS3KmuNsAD6mPvk-f16_4C8bzBqtgW1N-fSa4tYGW9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"All-around good restaurant! Great ambiance, friendly bartender (and great cocktails!), good dinner options. The service for seated dinner was slow, which is why I rated four stars - it took us a while to get drinks, even though the restaurant didn’t seem that busy. Regardless, would definitely recommend Raisa and looking forward to returning!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5FjEScS09p4sKoQY9XrPla3lJ54XRoMsJ7zdC&fid=0x0:0x7e87db22a9af0fbb"],"When":"2022-11-20"}]

[{"Name":"Krzysztof Kobiela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsx0CEEE8Z6bPVlGg3svNXmVYyXDG7PRy5PKon9sp_GwQurL6I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Something really good for young people. Food also is very tasty. Staff was very friendly and helpful. We spent there a few hours, and felt like at home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaKZT4OlFiG9-d1sVcnnhOxU16GFed-Hd06KSs&fid=0x0:0xce9e04c2ed55267e"],"When":"2023-6-11"},{"Name":"Dor-David Ashkenazi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKerGa747Fvng65mJGoWtFsQXRNEy7J8SOw-I2MtHqzG2xjFic=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here with friends at happy hour which is until 21:00 the drinks were good, we also ordered Adamame for sharing which was ok.
I ordered truffle toast that was delicious!
The prices were low because of happy hour dill so that is recommended to come at those hours.
The atmosphere is nice, gray music and people, there is also a dance bar inside which is more active at Thursday.
A great place to grab a drink and snacks with friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"GuyZa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqf9QNBbPnJ4Nz0CoE-uOfQrrfpzYC_51cxrh1btjK_AnmpLF1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was a nice place to grab a drink before catching a show. What is  really special is painting workshops that take place in the bar, it is great fun , painting and alcoholic drinks, what can go wrong 😀","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KC Mitch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkshOnyT8DwjyiaQNpQemj48As_KvIze9eZm3TVpNL0SfCkZ2m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food with lots of flavors this place we recommended and it will not disappoint. Friendly staff and central location. This place is a must.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMS9NuM4fVOPwtyoFr-ukI8jNX6qwxEdE0send5&fid=0x0:0xce9e04c2ed55267e"],"When":"2021-7-18"},{"Name":"Jonathan Gan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHYSmIZtqp4RNnfijEbV3Qg4dkmlrjgMeSpKNE3gLeOM008dde3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"A nice Israeli local bar in the heart of Tel Aviv. Not my first nor my second option. The cocktails weren't so good (how can you serve a decent cocktail as a juice?!). The music was okay. The service was nice. Prices are not cheap. No parking.
Try something else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gilad Levy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAT57Al0j_XfBq1C_VEVFSuGDEEIvV7FwA_g8ylSZRHE-fqW4Dpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Great happy hour!
However, the food is mediocre at best, music is 2 loud","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUNfb64UKL5rerWBqACTvgye4ARpUI9Xq9u71Q&fid=0x0:0xce9e04c2ed55267e"],"When":"2020-2-12"},{"Name":"Ari Mielnik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpvTd_1WhLDtV4sXhmNs85zQHosbarG1MI84KEGVHhAD2C6vBf6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It's ok if you sit outside. Inside the music is too loud, only good for people who don't enjoy any kind of conversation at all. Also, they think it's cool to waste thousands of papers every night throwing them to the people just to cause a shock effect. I think it's cheap, wasteful and bothering because it falls into your food and the already expensive drinks. The staff is not very friendly neither helpful but they are not unfriendly either. Having so many options in Tel Aviv, I don't see any reason to come back again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Jutrem Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNHje9et4Hk8UAb1pQgMEjg3d9vTG3vgUnXdhSD4xzBjB3YA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing place with good music, good drinks for a good prize, especially in happy hour! And it's super central. Right next to Dizengoff center, so it's easy to continue your night to where ever you need to go. It's a place where you can meet both local Israelis or also international students or tourists! Highly recommended for anyone looking for a good time at a cool bar.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Eli Dzialo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJPHvtm9y_iWpktR_PSk6Wxc-u8MS3bZAjicqAgiosCNLW7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super nice staff. Location is great and easy to find just near the Shuk. Look out for the Sunday offers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEtrfUPKhKbh-lq2ILQ4Gyg4aZqDNtfnwIJYwS&fid=0x0:0x1f2afcb088af1280"],"When":"2022-12-15"},{"Name":"אייר לין","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfFSAHbhMrIsTsBH_ph62jpzgmsP3nrEj3TGmaN86HyWaan4xWuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"-Overall: mixed experience. The food and desert menu is rather good for a pub and not too expensive. On the other hand many of the entries were missing. As a compensation we did get 2 free deserts
-Service is very kind
-Toilet was rather neglected, yet the sink was very pleasant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRzvjq3KnJnf2BLskoGGoRmP1X_83iOC54CXrG&fid=0x0:0x1f2afcb088af1280"],"When":"2016-8-17"},{"Name":"נריה","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTiOz88Qdm2HuZbjYlAmp3YNRyu73-8REURF0RwsA_JzROzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for evening drink, there is a balcony for smokers and indoor bar. The bar is normally packed, but with a waiting time of a few minutes you will find a place. Popular among students and ages between 20-45. There are two toilets in the powder room And it's  relatively clean.
Great fun people religious and non religious.
The service is good and fast.
A great place for drinks with friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phillip LaJoie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3jBtLdGTrKcPzktqfsNUPBOEyuHsbuQIRMUm7c-yD4NVehw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great time.  Music and crowd were both fantastic.  On the walk back ri the hotel we HAD to stop at a street food stand for what the sign indicated was the world's BEST falafel.  The sign didn't lie","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex gilenson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoJ25d9X6opTa966O3mCc9B4VsdIf8YlYj8sXkUOaKD4PNn0x0zg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jerusalem's classy bup. Funky place, designed very unique. Staff is nice, prices are fair. A nice place to hang out in the city center.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgNaLx6cVmkbDcaIOUBwRGCjYS9qZI2Dz0HwcN&fid=0x0:0x1f2afcb088af1280"],"When":"2018-8-14"},{"Name":"Offir Gonen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAPwPYfNWDHy9wtn3Kronl7voCbQRZB3kKrwk3lWdw6IR53pVF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yudaleh is the younger, more brassy, sister of Mahneyuda restaurant which is just across the sister. In yudaleh, which a resto-bar, you get to sit around the bar and drink a shot if alcohol with chefs and staff.
The atmosphere here is like the best party you've ever been and the food... Oh the food is unbelievable. The food is just as good as Mahneyuda but cheaper.
Overall a great energetic experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yossi Stern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdxbMXVy9yYQtBvhQelyGTuWw3jaAOF1UwyXBwbolHO6P6Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is of the hook I highly recommend avrybody to go to this bar!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxQvyxXE7ZzkzESLwp1qt-Zn0FaX6kygg3Ttz-&fid=0x0:0x1f2afcb088af1280"],"When":"2018-8-15"},{"Name":"yitz weiss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7EvKWcwE99xuu3QyMfFsTmuEe9b6nYBx54i8gKM3HAWWduFdKMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"chill bar with good vibes","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM076KKfpfI0G0L3HXFPwSDvTnKjtgSMGmB7BjU&fid=0x0:0x1f2afcb088af1280"],"When":"2023-3-18"}]

[{"Name":"Robert Amery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXedqaZD1FZmIQjejnSRrvOLmgGuR_n0LL9KzrPXx4YcYTDZ57t=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice restaurant,  kosher dairy and very tasty. Easy big car park and the restaurant we had to book ahead. We took the thai mix platter for 1st course, and an assortment of fish from the menu for our main course, and finally coconut ice cream, cream boulle and Ratatui ice cream.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXvX98apa3c3ktBy5kHcoj0cPvSeEO7hOd1iu5&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2022-5-1"},{"Name":"Galit Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5s26EYzun46Y2UbZvhRjWxS6ecH24U5FkKkLRy5AIiAuG8O-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Food was excellent, service quick.
One thing which I didn't like, we had to sit in a table for four, when we are five.
When I asked the waitress to add a table , she said you will manage....and refused to add a table.
The food was packed plate over plate, for the amount of money we paid it felt wrong,
Sitting in a fancy restaurant and eating like you sitting In a cheap dinner..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNt71eC6nrUWskEp_pa2NrIKR5gyRQGpvjRxVFc&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2022-5-10"},{"Name":"Shalev Moyal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL596dMJWmXKqvSg9wKsajiG_A6Qhse0WYe25XqSGvMTaZ4gEwh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful place! Everything is delicious and looks so good. The place itself is beautiful and quite fancy. The service is just great. Dishes are saved in no time. Very recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaN5Ntjf5r-S75NazxamKeYgdfOryERjvxRqxa&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2019-3-23"},{"Name":"Eitan Hajaj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL302Fx_R5aYY-uEhBZyK5ESdqvA41naUoE2p6snwm00NcAeA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food and service.
The place look great,
We came 13 people and really enjoyed our time there.
The dishes are big and not too expensive.
Very recommended, also it's kosher place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVIGteCCBrlv-n5szKKu-sxkkKbtwg8LsmWe8T&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2020-1-24"},{"Name":"Ronny van den Bergh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9g30xjQ-mf5Ue6NNvJ6rxvAiYFaDQ-oMapu0xS6DpCIOcXb-1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very nice food, but be aware the portions are huge. The garlic focaccia was delicious
Great service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO04elG-zli9aoafdZ8hxjIOh9F2I0B-Mw4OWIW&fid=0x0:0x7c308351dc704c03"],"When":"2022-5-20"},{"Name":"C E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvqCRMusPRjIlBbPUaWYxlWOjhzmsY0fod6P1vKjIkRnepUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I went on my birthday at this ‘’famous’’ restaurant that actually it was not what I expected.
Food it was average, same as in a pub or a night club.
The smell of the place was horrible, smell of toilet in all the restaurant.
They tried to put some spray but didn’t solve the issue.
Pasta was ok, but very expensive price.
The waiter was nice.
The place himself looks old and the plates could be more nice for this ‘’fancy’’place.
I felt like I am eating in some friend’s home, nothing special.
The garden of the restaurant it is nice.
I will never come back to this place and not send any people to it.
It’s an average place where you can spend time with family but in high prices.
You can really feel you are in a village.
Very disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkhrgRGnxe3Ir4zemEodlwp-Piacy9bcfRcrWNVcgUwU4PM9Y8uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst meal , presentation awful , service awful
Asked for a hot piece of fish and hot mash potato ,
Was served cold
When I complained it took 15 min of running around to make it right by that time was too late , was offered a plate of dessert that looked like a mess for compensation. Big let down as drove long way to visit this restaurant. 1/10 overall","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miriam Abrams (Deals Seeker)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpCI6M4smJet0N4YQALPUeZhisQnWj6yPX3n_ktW_KfQ9J83fK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stunning surroundings and atmosphere. I had an Israeli breakfast and the vegetables were absolutely delicious, so fresh everything was perfect, a very special place. And wonderful service. If you want to go to a unique place for a special occasion, this place is it for dairy, or Space for meaty.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Sam Aberman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW8LD98tdvZGX2GSpZHvoTTtCKd8qb17YM2nQsTU6mmb_xz9uN7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped in with a couple of friends for dinner just before Jewish New year.
The place was very quiet and we had an extremely attentive service and a very enjoyable evening with the place almost entirely to ourselves.
As many others have stated, the beer selection from across the globe, is fantastic.
We had plenty of explanation and recommendation for beer choice - we tried quite a few and can't say we were disappointed by anything that was recommended.
The food was also great. Large portions and reasonably priced.
Over all a great experience and highly recommended place to visit.
They were counting down days for Octoberfest beer festival. No doubt it will be a different and much more busy and likely even more fun experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmdRdOuPQ7gct4RuDF74tsEn8EViPSDTVAPkJo&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2022-9-28"},{"Name":"henry gild","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmjKKz2QMKMA8svIC-FZ0kXPgRWHebnWrbNpdcywgjM4ewhj-GKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Been there before with excellent service and food. This time the reception was lacking. I requested not to bring the main course until finished the starters and suddenly my wife order appeared. It was badly received  when I asked for it to be removed. I then received a total wrong order and when my order arrived it was not like previous times. On asking for a a salad they brought the wrong one and then removed it later returning it it as a takeaway.  The bill had items on it not ordered. The waitress was short tempered. Despite the fact that the food was good I will not return to Pinta nor recommend  it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Analiza Tirazona","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpg_3JlRjXVNa71HuGdTpLuUPcE7y08DvG-mzjcP5h6-d9ppl7gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went there to have my birthday lkunch, ,Service staffs are friendly, great  food, big  servings, good in house beers.. lovely place","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCB9eycYp17BY8bqakZttpGQQn0G51FGkVnUrO&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2022-11-17"},{"Name":"Julka Szczygiel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8ApcaeQIAZogSCSDFIQ_6STkQ56gaBuqh8KnaOm7-bmcz8UYU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best meat, lamb ribs were delicious, cesar salad also. Highly recomended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMnMKOgbegyiNJhTUyzBHzTFKhHFBSOQmyCwmJ&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2021-7-29"},{"Name":"Abigail Karpil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYCtfaCJ6pNF61IaPniEjDfeVUrQ0j521IW4YtSdOyjJ0kYw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place is nice has a unique pub-y like atmosphere. We visited the place before New Year’s and saw all the decorations coming up, very jolly. The prices are usual - same you could find in Rishon-Letziyon or Tel Aviv. Quality of the food was good. Service was slpw because there was only one lady serving that evening. We took the Grilled Salmon, which was a success, very recommended (89 shekels), the tongue, the shrimps which were also good. The baked potatoes were a little undercooked for me but that’s fixable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2G-gp0Qdh4c9ccdEkNQ_VwYiHC1DXtuNX4otd&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2021-12-17"},{"Name":"Eyal Shoshani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOKXqLplZ8jmFa2bIUZMueV210C5kqmX7dDjaz3IUWmn0WhVjLIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, friendly service, plenty of choices for everyone on the menu, and decent prices.
What more can you ask for?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0tWmOtnNJMLEjylXCQ4vtNXZnhn2Bu1udwAS8&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2020-1-30"},{"Name":"Yana Fesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqI_-aA8HbU1R1gvY-vGy2BMfVsdU57Q9eMMAqxnGURKWYgAFnPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy place, good for families as well as dates or dinner with friends. A big veriaty of beers, the dishes are also various anyone can find something they'll like from the menu.
The food is delicious, the service is attentive and timely.
This place isn't the cheapest, wouldnt call it budget place, but for the quality of the ingredients the prices are definitely not expansive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2rWV92m7wpTdnUv6Hm0j0Ia-3Q7qBrIIdRhEr&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2018-3-16"},{"Name":"Paul Smolkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf0fdurM5ZSWSg45KzcCdBH83yFzo27OSkPuNlLmpy05agX64p=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good variety of beer and food. For me the food is not really special or tasty. But have a lot of recommendations from friends, so, may be, it just me )) For sure, the place is worth to try and to make your own decision.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPD1k3N0PnQdz9lPSVvBZ6_WImSW_eTxkSVBtUD&fid=0x0:0x8af68f3aafebe741"],"When":"2018-3-19"}]

title: Pina Barosh - פינה בראש
descriptions: Charming rooms in an upscale guesthouse featuring a wine bar & a French restaurant, plus breakfast.
about: [{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]}]
user_reviews: [{"Name":"Nicole G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QeNj0UTN0yIrCGyJ0JhWwDODOg5QjAH0gdfB9Ji-oFl0zWFI-YVmhNAr-FGLycdpIjFmw=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"Pina Barosh was wonderful.  I stayed there with my mother and my aunt. Nili made us feel completely at home, and could not have been more welcoming.  The location was perfect for touring the Galilee region,and the view from the hotel is beautiful.  The rooms were comfortable and unique.  Breakfast was delicious.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brett O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QfHhPp0vyvo1Wo3WY4NH1G5QOPAHGBMv_XiebXLZtHzVwVa3wkRhb3dykyKrUCZPlawDA=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"Beautiful location with sweeping view of the valley from the dining area. Has the character of a very old building with all the modern needs. The manager is extremely pleasant and goes  to any length to make your stay wonderful. We needed some glasses to have drinks with our friends and she meticulously cleaned and wiped each glass. Property is beautiful with many nooks for quiet reflection.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Avi Kessler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCutlsrJMh9RcUhQlGIQg6vbquaBs-dmLDzfVV3c8pgSSCWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There is Rosh Pina before Corona and Rosh Pina after Corona. Rosh Pina has still not recovered from Corona. There used to be places open in the evening serving a nice dinner. No more, maybe a truck if you are lucky. Pina baRosh was once one of those great establishments that ppl used to come a long way for. I would fly up here to eat breakfast in this place and then fly back to Tel-Aviv.\nI drove up here with the wife this time to be at a wine festival in Ramot Naftaly. Breakfast was ok. Service left much to be desired. This is true in many places in Israel. The view however from this place is still to die for. Give it a shot...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEDad8eHUqBD2OX6BC97taqbZh7hhaR-gAad84\u0026fid=0x0:0x13396909d82c2eff"],"When":"2023-6-6"},{"Name":"Udi Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwozTD9HNjYLj2MpsBYuwchPV4HcHW6C9dZrpt-1NkqUVq-NBs2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service with a smile and the readiness to assist is the great hallmark of this lovely , pleasant place.The rooms/ suites are comfortable albeit a bit old and it is evident that some update need to take place.Nevertheless ,the court that all rooms are facing, the garden and specially SHIRI BISTRO, the establishment's restaurant , make up big time for the rooms' lack of up to date feel.Still, the places ooze character  and if you haven't been there before, don't miss the vue from the garden or the restaurant- simply amazing, specially mount Hermon to the north, covered with snow in winter.Breakfast should be mentioned as a big highlight, tasty and wonderful experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anne b","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0QdrOaBwvzVCVZGa_JCxmRob18-RTGR2NAc2ehM2ioIFQuUJBtaO6jr7GHqX15LV00VYsw=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"My husband and I had been looking forward to staying at Pina Barosh for several years (pandemic put it all on hold for awhile) and it was worth the wait when we finally arrived last month for a 3 night stay. You don't get more friendly, welcoming and helpful than Merom, who greeted us when we walked into the informal check in area. ||||We had heard about Pina Barosh from others who had stayed there and it was everything we expected and more. Beautiful stone rooms and garden areas, photo-worthy and delicious breakfasts, a friendly staff, great music selections from a speaker on the terrace and the terrace itself where meals were served. Since dinner isn't served here since the pandemic, we just loved hanging out at the peaceful terrace at night listening to the music, looking out at the lights towards the Golan. ||||The bed and breakfast is located across from the Baron's Garden and the old city is a short walk uphill. We absolutely loved this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janet K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/local-reviews/AJMZ0Qdx0CtChWdL4amzhVtedU6JgNzs3A9KzPS8K998c7-u-mDeTb-7WQwuTD-PPX6BcVA5wg=s120-c-br100","Rating":0,"Description":"This was one of the most pleasant stays I’ve had in a Bed and Breakfast! The stone walkways, flowers and just atmospheric is wonderful. The views are amazing. I encourage you to try to get the deluxe suite. They gave us a lovely basket for breakfast along with made to order eggs and there was enough to pack for a picnic lunch! We didn’t see much staff and I would suggest to management to circle around occasionally and when they do, they should speak to guests or at least nod! I think it will just take time for business as usual after COVID. I would recommend staying here and we will be back for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miryam Elisheva Honigman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRNgeW_i0m4IO2KQ1sCsjLOVsnEYwV4HeQZ43LA89ucp7fqVfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. Spent many days \u0026 nights over a course of 7 years at this place. My home away from home. Rustic Quiet charm and the family that owns it are wonderful.  Staff will go out of their way to assist at all possible. Food presentation is delightful and the food is delicious. Price and selection is good, atmosphere is off the charts if you r looking for something romantic, quiet and a  Israeli experience with true comfort, u must experience this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5k2mP3LHH7tvpZcRlcfFaCKJTs4vc-KyIxnEl\u0026fid=0x0:0x13396909d82c2eff"],"When":"2020-6-23"},{"Name":"Nati Yakunina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2ZRyxpBFyf-69fHZ270s3B4iQB7GTzvAkwYH0psuwL_zQ6Rx_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Marvellous view, it's like ,a piece of Italy in Israel. We stopped just for a cup of tea and sweet treat, the food is delicious. This place is in my list, I will definitely come back there.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Yishay Yovel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaEZHOm_aSJKjjiA8Ggq-rsAXmd2oAfLJNmbc1IVqGLtxYvJaHlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best restaurants in Israel. The menu was intriguing and the food was amazingly executed. The flow and pace of the meal was just right and the service (thanks, Niki) was knowledgeable and pleasant. The meal is expensive, basically what you would expect in a Michelin star restaurant. It should get one.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emanuel Rosenzweig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHEtyWTSJdlcICnd8GjGKdjdHaNRtCInfdFQPGNNUMyL5NUIy0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best restaurants in Israel. Every single dish has its own unique interpretation and style. Clever play with flavors and textures.
The service is professional and the overall experience is fantastic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTGhZGtJJ_npATfjqKPXBuxx58rRUvfpcGnSik&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-5-21"},{"Name":"Kris T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3_tCK-Xbxvwi7N_hWz2mAcoaAIkny1d9vDhcl74Bug6Fn0VpSJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I heard so much about this restaurant and expected more. Waiters were getting the orders wrong and forgetting things; food was expensive and meat was great but some of the other dishes and deserts were average. Sea tartar was so full of coriander that killed all other taste, and it was not even mentioned in the ingredients. Atmosphere was ok but also more on the basic side. Lack of attention to details or creating exclusive experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOin-CavBzuM9MuK95763H7uxYpK6ZqsVwIqVhV&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-9-20"},{"Name":"Alex Okin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIONNgRLxqCFEuNgE8MgvvtzFokpgoZmiJIz7ekT1zGkmaflg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Starting with the service, we were served by Nikki who was exceptional. Explained everything to the last detail, and took care of everything we needed. The food was incredible, unique combinations and flavor bombs. Honestly I don't have a specific recommendation, just order a couple of each section. This was a great experience and we will definitely come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvHKuTBob2NOCkJ2eEi-Cu38PMAdMyeDUbzN-c&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-7-21"},{"Name":"Mai Srugo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBddj7_zQu_3wyy4y4YYMelHs5mnekghXCvOTw_eF4dHyx7A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the city's absolute gems!
Entering through the boutique Hotel Drisco, you're immediately transported to a Parisian-like ambiance. The dining experience here is exceptional, with every bite feeling like a dream.
I highly recommend trying their gnocchi, which is like fluffy clouds, and their lobster pasta. The atmosphere is truly unique, adding to the overall amazing experience.
It's worth noting that the prices are on the higher side, but the exceptional quality justifies it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMs56ZDHRayXwRx1a2EwCnfSS6Ouk-cNvh5qdgb&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-8-21"},{"Name":"Yael Shenhav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLPMeB1uP-Azs3EnfgzmtDCXLB431LQADyOKG0uDiEongAE1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good fine dining restaurant - some interesting dishes , Mediterranean flavors , lots of fish dishes and good service . Only downside is one of the specials was a Rascasse fish - full of fish bones for only few bytes of fish . Prices are high - not unlike similar restaurants in Tel Aviv","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPHZa3YJHbxLeL6vcjGeHdhzEghhswB4R7Szt7&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Leeju Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqao1CBoep44_FnGR8xITCm928QEps6jD5-3n4X0MREayY7MSO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been trying chef restaurants in tel Aviv, from time to time.  George and John has very nice service and food is just delicious.  I would highly recommend if you guys are looking for delicious and unique combination. Ofcourse the price are higher then normal restaurants with small portion but trust me you would not regret by spending money there. 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyOrh4scp9cuFY6GN1Ur3o1CgxsoT-Ky4f3C4&fid=0x0:0xd72f878298a9af5d"],"When":"2023-9-7"},{"Name":"Tal Lichtenstein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSiGfsuYyLIaJubz7R0pJhj1CwIB3DOmWZQOVeSMdyhiL_oq8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We visited for breakfast. The good - everything was very tasty and fresh. The disappointing - the variety has dropped considerably since our visit about a year ago: Breakfast now consists of a main dish (omelette, bedict, etc), six tiny dishes of fish/cheese/spread samples that are not refilled, and a buffet that has a veg. salad, spreads, butter and bread/pastries. Everything was of high quality, but we would have expected some more for the price they charge. There are definitely better options in the area.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Hilary Mawia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBuh9NV__P0sOdxiYRc8KVA3uldQXvMQmuOY3qPKM8LIJHCaCh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Portions are small but it is reasonable for the lower price point. The seafood mix in cream sauce was perfectly made. And the largest pour of wine I've ever had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXRWj9Ej3qtG2cfk9KPnTi9FA5jnqxl28ZuUJ-&fid=0x0:0x30dbb8c5231d14f9"],"When":"2023-3-27"},{"Name":"Ayal Avisar (Aylo)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9YHT-MCy2hJVlGHOUec8VQYTeHFyB_c9lZb8xoBS6JjJjAPEU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good variety of grilled meats and fish.
Food was ok.
Good for families, groups, couples.
Service wasn’t good. Long waiting time.
Price is not cheap nor expensive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeNl5xaV0clUOoRw-k__cofSjWWdVxnieZ1Ijn&fid=0x0:0x30dbb8c5231d14f9"],"When":"2021-9-8"},{"Name":"דניאל ברון","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJnzIBDBRfkEgyzlCHKy4X5qwJ3P__D_EV65ZNugZVNU0nzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good restronaut.
The food is very tasty and the price is nice.
We had seafood mix with gravy, pork mix , pork barbecue, salad and baby meal that includes sausages with salad.
All the food was great and worth the money!!
The waiter was also very kind and fast.
Outside their is also a playing place which our son really enjoyed.
If you are in Ashkelon and your hungry I recommend you to visit the place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXRfxVscqME6hNz-45v5QZHeuOuTzVeFteHPFz&fid=0x0:0x30dbb8c5231d14f9"],"When":"2021-10-9"},{"Name":"Michael Sturm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOudAYvipxoJ44YQtBTbre10XwbUQsLFAlLSozzHG9Angp8XDv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid self service restaurant for meat lovers. The meat is cooked fresh....kebab tastes really good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNiJhOmkGEkvyrgaCj72UIXuy9MvpAb0jfsooT&fid=0x0:0x30dbb8c5231d14f9"],"When":"2019-4-28"},{"Name":"Jamal Qawasmeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKVfsetR6N8bgZlNJwU56tl7nFaa3EzYXSpj_BCw1a2UNlPNkb4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good food , self-service","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6NMkrSqJvqKPJ8L5VNMq0jmMHk7C1XnPIZpLh&fid=0x0:0x30dbb8c5231d14f9"],"When":"2023-7-1"},{"Name":"Ran Ben-David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKl_p93F1RGIg28kAp1geMocCkjaiT-YDDeSxUpEuYu87MuQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"24/7 Very good grill food, not cheap!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0R6FYjmbjBKwiv4CpI2aJ-4iJ5icZbuLBqQVe&fid=0x0:0x30dbb8c5231d14f9"],"When":"2020-8-1"},{"Name":"Denis Zoubarev","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUy9k6yS-7bl4kpmMe7KVWQmVWg9W7irUmq2A6z3ORI4xEQyN2O=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Its a modest restaurant that is held by russians. It delivers very good meat for a decent price and on top of it, the resraurant works 24/7 24 hours a day. Priceless. I put -1 star just because at nights its got a self service rule.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Simonov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVm5BfHVPEs2qk3XyyimwkrIAO4LBTb0YMPg_KjSAWlklWBrCdV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a nice place for familes. The food is good (not kosher though) and it is always open. There is a self dine section (you order food from the cashier and preper the table yourself, i.e no waiter) and there is a section where (which looks nicer) you receive a waiter which brings all of your food. All in all, i've been coming to this place for years now and I've never left hungry or unstisfied.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Vasil Khachiashvili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDop7ADn65OKesSnE6fah_UfbslSyP2WKvwgyw-NP2NgTDVZd2MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place !!! Great food, good music !!!
Most Delicious FISH AND CHOPS Ever !!!!
I Have tried it at many places around the world here they are the best!!! And also SHRIMPS in cream and garlic souce are amazing !!! YOU SHOULD TRY !!!

Edit: They Renewed Menu, and again its awesome !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeUE2kJQY4MfxQ4XOjADagmUlYLodejYBytwhX&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2018-12-7"},{"Name":"Samuel Samuelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAUD7Mv8-xUd6gcM2_CzZXtwQjTyuG_RWvGV8GNx18KQhzUMZ4CA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands down the best place to hang out in Ashkelon. Sitting right on the beach gives it a great relaxed vibe during the day, and at night it livens up with loud music for a younger crowd. Great food (that's not just limited to appetizers) is sure to please, but a wide selection of beer and liquor sets it apart from even the best restaurants in Israel. Whether you're looking for a family friendly place to eat lunch, or a raucous bar to burn the midnight oil, Archie's Public House does not disappoint.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpppyIRWK1P1T1NyKFvIaVmUgvjB_NLwxIv2fD&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2017-1-27"},{"Name":"Elchin Abdullayev","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdxdmcsDFXEEvoKPqTNaEAmCxzo0YZvKxxmH3p1ymO9astoh4J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maybe one of the best pub-style restaurants in Ashkelon. Eqplant was great as was fish & chips. Perfect fast service, nice people. Next to the beach.
5* all around.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSZ2KIuDaeBqEoFHw-azHSoB9WVwl5SaIBgHoo&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2023-4-11"},{"Name":"David Kliger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSYa7IkE8WK_f9fEXJxqCVRDV2J0fJid5M1Iuqu2U_uDfeAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place!!!
Superb atmosphere, lovely service and the food was delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtL_Ay9ci5mwHJNS4u1zvUGwdWaG7gpf87Fbnu&fid=0x0:0x1a970b27ff9b84c7"],"When":"2023-2-17"},{"Name":"Ron Breger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWi1PvL1F-2_INDwEHu0eRXNNpj869-Z87VkfpJNgPu-rgA220mSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place with great food. The staff is nice and friendly :)
Ordered poached eggs with bacon and it was really good!
The atmosphere reminds me an European one, as well as the food.
Their burger is amazing! Had it with cheddar, onion butter and roast beef and it was wonderful.
Really recommended, both on a Friday night and on a casual day!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yogev Ainhoren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEOrd2_dHOfd1qFxDXdTL7sN66xA2Ud7wSg4DjqQnlHANXvKMajg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had great special burger. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Momma Eds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQdVrHlH2YtWEA3wpu8dEuDQOddQEaXPC4K8H7-CxnelQAUCWIYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place has a very romantic atmosphere, but unfortunately, it's not suitable for people with disabilities, especially those in wheelchairs, as there are no ramps available. One of the staff members suggested that we sit outside, but it wasn't comfortable for us because of the hot weather.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0gJp7ZTtEcJnUD8_wuPvCqKu8qQA_U2O1bAOb\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2023-8-2"},{"Name":"Olga S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW710c91TebkQA9N1tsDaki1qn-Xn0Q2bhq8cQH9NyxCIwD7xUt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place to have a romantic dinner or to spend an evening with family. The food is delicious, the steak is awesome. You have to try it with garlic butter sauce. No matter what you order it will be amazing. The restaurant itself is very beautiful and the music creates a very calm atmosphere. The staff is very nice and kind. I have enjoyed my dinner very much🙂","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfyQOqeygPafhXtnqNpcB1x_DLJY0tD7qzwzCO\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2023-6-15"},{"Name":"DongKoo Kim (DreamDK)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRoMiXRD7JzMzpP9RXi2RPC7oCEdf7mnjtVQ2Eza2RD346UcwZEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wonderful place! Nice and cozy! Very retro style atmosphere! Delicious foods and all my friends loved. Lovely person served us with big smile.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGpvwzID2kxN0AQhDtTqhkkjTDVc9b1ruuMVVV\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2023-7-21"},{"Name":"john wilkes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJzRiQ5Z6SycvafZY3xXm1zcV8Rwm-Goxr5Gnsc3iGRfYAH_iVVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gourmet food: a cut or two above the typical tourist fare that is so common in Tiberias. Ample portions (despite what other reviewers may say!). Good wines. Friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKDEYz2WeDLpwwSERQALN-X2U0vMB95HsThAP-\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2022-6-16"},{"Name":"Michael Kupermann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVh6c2JqEN_ns-xypjnDZaHxX042e-ww7dC2sqRPDuPYrCqucoh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are 3 weeks in Israel and traveled the country. This restaurant is so far the best one. You have to try the Eggplant Rolls, the homemade bread, roasted Paprika and all from the menu! Thumbs up for this culinary island in Tiberias!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeTeG6z6mju8cRxpe4WY5Cpdwxe-tb9ncI5w0\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2022-7-18"},{"Name":"Jack Roldan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMPZAeyFfrqQnTOF_3kRa7VTWQh5esahJbZk0eRW7EYdOmcC70=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Second visit here,  I thing short of consistency 8 years later. Great service, food was delicious and the experience just fantastic. Highly recommend.  Everything is good. Try the lamb! I will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6DlM-VhGoVH7XstUHZ6bvyhMyitg7UC_HKxIM\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2022-10-5"},{"Name":"mariusz urbanczyk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoFs-_MzbTOsO7YYW100pWkGh-Ae8QyrrHDq6KGm9WevLhkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Decent food but overpriced for what it is. The starters were very nice we had aubergine and garden salads. Both fresh and good well flavored. For the main we had beef fillet and a local fish. Both were fresh but lack distinctive flavor. If you feel like splashing on wine I suggest Yarden cabaret from 2015 that will set you back by additional 50 euro but it’s a good bottle of wine. The service was nice and attentive but the restaurant doesn’t deliver on the value proposition when it comes to decor, atmosphere for the price they are asking for the experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdjXS4k9s4ELHjhUJQVsfnuZ0qO86LjNFvXtF8\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2019-3-18"},{"Name":"Jeff Goldstone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZtYNzzv4OfbkfuqGt0RB5O9jHnLZi2ckVXrXq80Nq4F5xr5hJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great lunch at Little Tiberias and recommend it when you’re in the city! The food was exceptional, the service was wonderful. The appetizers, the main course and the desserts were fantastic!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVY-B1d26k0qGihVQ6jMzQF5oijGAAnjEWKbV9\u0026fid=0x0:0xffc0beca7ea4c4d7"],"When":"2022-7-27"}]

The cuisine from republic of Georgia and a bit of Russian mixed in. Everything was delicious. Starting with hachapuri adjaruli - a cheese stuffed bread boat, and hinkali meat stuffed juicy dumplings, followed by a simple salad, and culminating in shish kebab with side of fries and assortment of pickled vegetables. [{"Name":"Liel Ilyaev","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1IAgJIbjSw9j--Y-HvrMZnR8kkyBVplh0dk1m5H7Y2FlBnt2PbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here with my sister and my nephew for a stroll in the park day and sat here around the afternoon for dinner and had very good meal including pizza, rizotto, cocktails and a chocolate cake 💕 staff were friendly, there was a place to charge my phone 🙏 and quite busy but definelty has enough place for a small group 🤙 food is definelty, when the pizza wasn't cut we had to cut it ourselves but we got a cutting knife from the server/waiter no problem , nice view to the lake in front and nice greenery/garden surroundings 💕","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuCmbRXg-rZhCGmDwCAFAeUYD5d4rWIOsNv5eg&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2023-10-2"},{"Name":"Guy Wolt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXL2Xfmq6VuR_fI-xEaprIbj9SrroXjFpG2MpC0-Xg4Q6IB7KBOVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Cozy place. We sat outside, and it seemed too crowded for my taste, but the service and food were delightful. Pricey but high-level dishes. It seems the chef knows what he's doing. We'll definitely return but might sit inside.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tal M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoI5hV6uQm17P-_qsoeONKWfCrLayCv3wDqAUpQY1n3Qv9CQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very unique setting in the park with ducks around. Israeli breakfast just perfect with the Israeli dips, good bread, good coffee. Shakshooka is so good and so is the polenta. Homemade strawberry jam at the end sealed it. But mainly the most friendly staff and tranquil setting. Only had breakfast. Dinner is next","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Waad Jz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuzigNB_qh8IIHNOTACjRXXGibklAP25y-Q1qjCZFZ4P8d64e3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place for couples and friends 🌹.

The workers were very friendly, kept checking on us, also helped us cut the pizza 🍕😅.

The food was good, we ordered a sicilian tomato sauce pasta with cheese 🍝, pizza margherita 🍕 and a green salad with pears and nuts 🥗. The pasta and the salad were great, however the pizza wasn't that good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_XhLJFyIWcWMkuKXFyA2281dbXDjlDcfc1q5d&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2023-5-28"},{"Name":"Dmitry Kopin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWT8sILsCZ49bTwFShAFnVWnNkQy1x1AxKgbGmb1_ayV1oIbI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The hostess informed us that there were no available seats in the interior of the establishment, despite the fact that there were indeed seats available. We repeatedly expressed our discomfort with the outdoor seating due to the high temperatures and requested that the air conditioning unit be moved closer to our table. However, we were politely informed that it was not possible to relocate the air conditioning unit from another table, which was equipped with three air conditioning units.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dani shemesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdgSl_GRV7eyiNlwct0sd-OjxjjMkJWc70QeJg446SMTwJiL1d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"TL;DR the only coffee place in the park.

Joy garden has a winning location overlooking the lake.
There are tables inside and outside under  big ficus trees where you can enjoy the park air in spring and fall.

We got there for a late breakfast since it's the only place to buy food/drinks in the park. It's always full and you need to reserve a table ahead of time.
We got seated outside and got the menus right away.
We ordered:
- Breakfast for one - omelet with salads, bread bucket and a drink.
- Croque madam - a fried egg in a bagel with cheese.
- Porridge with fruits on top.
- Cappuccino and Americano to help us wake up :)

We got the drinks right away but the service is very slow there we waited over 30 min for the food, but the weather was good so we took our time.
The drinks were good but the food was medium - that's what happens when you have no competition .
The prices are fair - 180 nis tip inclusive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKcC0I7eGK_PKeDNoIEVs6gzzPrbUbWhfdywmQ&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2022-4-29"},{"Name":"Marc Berman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2KT2XvYKolgMxa38doiRuKpqkNNKD3XWZdAH2ziRwTpuLDlgHqA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This hidden gem tucked away in the middle of a huge park has views looking over a lake and offers both a breakfast and dinner menu based on fish and dairy products. We arrived for breakfast and ordered the classic shakshuka, croque madame, Turkish pastry with spinach and the lentil, mushrooms and sweet potato salad. All 4 dishes were excellent and the accompanying side dishes were a nice touch. The bread was fresh and hot and the coffee finished off one of the best breakfast experiences here in Israel. We are looking forward to returning soon to experience the new evening fish menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdyahsF4xaizl2WnLJF1r-VNB9I_5dImo502rN&fid=0x0:0x20328ed744140eba"],"When":"2023-7-11"},{"Name":"Ron Kitay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPbUGSYHwl7X6gHKMXkMbAvFwBspn6MvFflelRiJ3FN6bhVPgLug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was tasty and fresh, the service was kind and attentful and the atmosphere was pleasant - we enjoyed our breakfast very much and we will definitely return.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Or Rochlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0YBwdznWqgmMI6rzYUua-ajTJRwnKhqZojQ4P6vOpO8I9vb4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Magdalena! One of the best restaurant in the Galilee. Modern cuisine with local Arab touch. The restaurant is very beautiful and the atmosphere is very peaceful. The service is excellent and the food is so delicious! ;)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPY1cpfk724SEoYxoJDQJtpwDoavwsV_MZs-D4&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-4-5"},{"Name":"Ami Giz Guided Tours","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCFpPPQJPodlzCRRbz9kXyHFOM5igB_KmMJx4K7DTFwr2zwele_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favorite restaurant by the Sea Of Galilee .
As an Israeli Tour Guide i love it and always bring my tourists here ,try and share large variety of dishes.
Enjoy!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRfzlvYSWe-X-H2kQnASbOmt9SpktZuoVr9dV7&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2022-12-6"},{"Name":"Roy Latke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUibr29cj0e-T6n24qKODTYwbdPVIN7L6f7NPALV9YmuKG1rKsAGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My 3rd time here and it’s always a win. Variety of amazing dishes. If you're with a group, consider get all the first dishes and share them","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnk9BQ8uzJvU3XG9SlZdkrdaq8crlME9ry2m4Q&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-7-20"},{"Name":"Ronny On","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6u8sBC-9dLuJitjwXB4wuwg4cMGtERSxlI1WcL6gnuDRNlHDV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One is the best restaurants in the area!
Their dishes are original and always delicious, with a huge variety of amazing first courses.
The service is as professional as it gets, friendly and attentive to your needs and special requests.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWWZoL2BddMSxeKWbLbpMEJknl3Z4ZUCDJhqD2&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-4-9"},{"Name":"Yuval K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhu_BtuT6xVPhpaH-uRPhJ82PKXuXCxJ17XcBQ8qilTX6ZFWrLg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fabulous! It all starts with excellent service. From our own waitress and others. Pleasant service yet knowledgeable and not pushy. Then comes the delicious food. We had 12 dishes in total. The firsts were all great. The arais, the mushrooms, the goose liver and others all fantastic. We had two main dishes. The lamb chops are amazing. The fish less. From the desserts we loved the katayef with is fried dough with nuts and other good things. Beautiful restaurant and great food and service. It's a must!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPolPZ3h7ARtSpHyK43TGgLEWt1wQkSdGvuVz3&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2022-8-15"},{"Name":"Shame A Name","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6ovtiiDllWWnf5Z7F9T06lTsE3OfoYT8LgQbQ0GRbfiGeVgGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had lunch here on the way to River Jordan from Capernaum. The food is of very good quality. The fish was fresh and the lamb meat was well seasoned and properly cooked that it remains juicy. Staff were helpful and our main meals were served altogether as you would expect in a premium restaurant.  We spent 2 hours here as we enjoyed the setting and the view.  In terms of price, you would expect to pay a bit more considering the area and the ambience this restaurant provides.  We had a fantastic meal.  The restaurant is located on the upper floor, lift on site.  The toilets were clean in keeping with the premium feel.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgBYEXqO2EXqWRoBU5X6JRnxeQTVMWx9ylMS0M&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2019-11-4"},{"Name":"Itzik levy (Izikl)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMhOPtKPne5dwZdLYeB-7gSBitO9rV3432q_evRYLwaOfT2JvsFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chef's Restaurant.  Restaurant in front of it on Route 90. Reservations are required in advance, especially on weekends.  The service is excellent.  Beautiful and special dishes.  Istanbul sticks, cigars stuffed with cheese.  Lamb chops, amazing.  Excellent borta salad, tomato pieces and mozzarella.  Very expensive prices","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgBc9UEuPbuezLN5eivdFWr9tnlIj2Qq12G5gV&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2023-8-6"},{"Name":"Haim Molcho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7cgN3oNbwgHSAT05ArPhZ-ZSASMM0ZwRKJ7M9Ju9VLKZSJM8HXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent restaurant with excellent service. The first courses are very tasty and special, quite large to share. The main courses may be less unique, but tasty and large. Our waiter was eager to help with vegan dishes.
The desserts are unusual, especially the “Malabi cannoli” and “Lebanese nights”.
The price is reasonable in relation to the quality and quantity.
We’ll be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGCrx46lpLX2yI16uIu1Dj_w2sVNJ3L5SaxZPT&fid=0x0:0xb9a103aabe9f3e0"],"When":"2022-6-24"}]

[{"Name":"Maor Alkobi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiw29AVvFkWWLUbXe9u1VnZnz5A2PzY2Yua9SGbZnBeTpsEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The vibe and drinks was great! So is the hookah and the location is amazing (beach front), I wouldn’t order any food there as it tasted much like bar food, I would give the food 1/10. The service is not great but that’s what happens when you include service as part of the check, the waiters really don’t care about customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZULxDogiL6N75ZMU4zIukWBTcdyni2PfSwFHO&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2022-10-13"},{"Name":"Yaron Shemesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmh7cDE4nAQOeOrzMs-KuHFHfsdoPVDN2Sx79Yqyk_ipwLph5VuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service was OK. The food was OK. We waited for sometime to get the check but was told some people were in shift about 15 hours so understand (not sure this is ok from labor point...). The service of 10% (usually I leave more than 15%), was already included in the bill mentioned there as optional but this fact was never mentioned by the them when charged my credit card. I almost doubled my tip.
Bottom line,  food and place location are OK, cost is reasonable. Make sure to review the check and see that tip is included so not leave double.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOJaotvM1hMBclEQJUwDD5la_vLC2m0UcYGnx6&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2021-8-9"},{"Name":"Larytet.android Larytet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKey9-XNJ0HTkU4mz5KqSKyIEnxJ7gPuRO7__wlGkjzbDsfCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Petra in Ashdod is a place where the setting truly shines. With its prime location right by the sea, you’re treated to a beautiful evening sun descending over the water—an ambiance that’s hard to beat. The menu is a sprawling 15 pages long, full of vibrant images—a culinary tour for those who can’t decide on just one destination.

As for the food, it’s decent. There are certainly better, hmmm,  culinary experiences to be found in Tel Aviv, and yes, some might find a few dishes a bit on the, for missing a  better word, simple side. However, it’s unlikely you’ll leave dissatisfied. Even my kids, who consider themselves in, despite a few grumbles, were quietly focused on their meals for a good 20 minutes.

In the end, Petra offers a well-rounded experience. The view, and the atmosphere ensure a pleasant evening out. It’s an experience that leaves me feeling that less than 5 stars wouldn’t do it justice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nina Strelets","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDzoH18VpyecJKWJlDxFtGMA9GrJJVF0oHUdYTajvgY8gNJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Petra in Ashdod offers a decent dining experience with a lovely view of the sea. While the food is satisfactory, the real highlight is the scenic backdrop. A solid choice if you're looking to enjoy a meal with a beautiful view. By the way, they automatically charge 10% tip for the service. Total rating: 3.6/5 .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alina Gurevich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJxY7xgSTZ1cx1oZRchCSpqEHb98Nml2B0b3FOHbjQMyKbmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We made same day reservation for this place to celebrate my birthday with a family. It was Friday evening. However,  when we arrived nobody could find our names on the reservation list. It was very busy with big line of people trying to get in. And very loud music.  Thankfully we had saved recorded audio of making reservations and finally we were sitted. We told about my birthday when reservation been made and also right away to our waitress.  I saw other people celebrating with waitstaff bringing them desert with sparklers and singing for them.  It looked like fun and I was expecting to have the same. We ordered food and were waiting for at least some glasses for water. Food was good,  portions are huge. We ordered khachapuri among the other dishes,  but it didn't arrive till almost the end of our dinner.  We thought it was forgotten and it would be OK, since we were full already,  but it arrived by the end. During the dinner we were hunting for waitstaff,  since nobody came to check on us. Another waiter came by and we again asked for a birthday special.  We ordered desert only for this reason.  And when another waiter brought desert, he just put it on the table and left.  No birthday song , no sparkle,  no nothing. I was so upset. And at same time we saw someone else is celebrating properly.  Finally our waitress showed up to bring our bill. We told her what happened,  she just looked surprised,  turned around and left. No apology at all, no care. I wouldn't even tip her, but tips already included in bill. We were so disappointed. I feel upset even 2 days later.  Very bad experience.  We won't come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"George Mack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIom1q9dFpBY_paUNMh2iAuxMhVYBbU2sLOB5nTHTg6eCjYyg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic views across the Mediterranean. Wonderful big breakfast and halloumi cheese filled calamari. Must visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdZq0N3d7zeKqgeCXAvtwkIsZYR5vy4oaNxEoe&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2023-10-5"},{"Name":"David Feldman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8BH6O7EpD2tADa5qwE-dS-1J0sOxSGWEZ3lfylHYN8dedoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My 3rd visit in two years. Overall I like the place and the food. The traditional Georgian dishes are great. Not cheap but portions are huge (share).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhwSEyV5_prks072sKt6ZcMEZrktJpUXFomEa2&fid=0x0:0x1a0f020f1e1670d1"],"When":"2018-12-22"},{"Name":"Vasil Khachiashvili","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDop7ADn65OKesSnE6fah_UfbslSyP2WKvwgyw-NP2NgTDVZd2MA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is full with very delicious Georgian food.
